        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued July 12 at 12:57PM EDT by NWS Blacksburg VA</headline>
        <description>At 1257 PM EDT, Doppler radar was tracking a strong thunderstorm over
Buffalo Ridge, or near Woolwine, moving east at 10 mph.

HAZARD...Half inch hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor hail damage to vegetation is possible.

Locations impacted include...
Woolwine...
Sanville...
Fairy Stone State Park...
Buffalo Ridge...
Philpott Dam...
Charity...
and Patrick Springs.
</description>
        <instruction>If outdoors, consider seeking shelter inside a building.</instruction>
